Selenium class 5:

Handling checkboxes(u can select multiple options) and radiobutton(we can select only one):
-- if you have only one checkbox or radiobutton you cna just click on in
--if you have multiple chooses we gonna store them in the list and loop through

DropDowns:

DropDown is a menu whitch gives us opportunity to select one or more options
Types of DropDowns:
1.Single select
2.Multiple select

Handling dropdowns:
1.click on dropdown and click on the option
2.Using select class
            in order to use select class we need to
            make sure our dropdown has selected tag

Selecting an option from a dropdown can be done in 3 ways:
1.By index
2.By visible text
3.By value

Wherewer you interract with multiple elementl you store them inside the container such as List,Set...


